#: ../apt-setup:454
msgid ""
"You probably used a CD to install the Debian base system, but it is not "
"currently in the drive. You should probably just insert it and select \"cdrom"
"\"."
msgstr ""
"Mwy na thebyg, defnyddioch CD er mwyn sefydlu system sail Debian, ond nid yw "
"yn y gyrriant ar hyn o bryd. Mae'n debyg mai'r peth gorau yw i'w rhoi e i "
"fewn a dewis \"cdrom\"."

